title: 177: The Costco Haul Episode (August '22 Edition)
itunes:title: The Costco Haul Episode (August '22 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa, Jamie, and Mikey taste-tested some very interesting and creative finds, like chicken sausage protein bites, grilled fajitas rajas, a new stir-fry from Kevin’s Natural foods, super yummy steamed buns (aka bao), cherry tomato crisps, and a whole lot more! Plus, the find of the entire haul: an OUT OF THIS WORLD matcha lemonade mix. Wait no more—push play now, then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the finds mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: Time for another Costco Haul, and this one will not disappoint!
